Toy transport network data

Source: R/data.R
toy_transport_network.Rd

Note that this dataset requires the sf package to work properly. This dataset contains street network within some SA2 zones of Melborune CBD, Australia in a sf::sf format. This network is contained within the boundaries of toy_zones.

toy_transport_network

Format

A sf::sf data frame with 11 rows and 14 variables:

id

(integer()) zone id

nb_lanes

(integer())

speed

(double())

capacity

(double())

rd_type

(integer())

fnode

(double())

tnode

(double())

geometry

(list())

length

(double())

See also

toy_zones
